import React from "react";
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row';
import Col from "react-bootstrap/Col";
import InputGroup from 'react-bootstrap/InputGroup';
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';

function Login(){

    return <Row>
    <Col lg={{span: 6, offset: 3}}>
    <Form>
        <Row>
            <Col lg={{span: 2, offset: 5}}>
                <InputGroup>
                    <Form.Control placeholder="電郵" className="emailInput"></Form.Control>
                    <InputGroup.Append>
                        <InputGroup.Text>@hohsc.org.hk</InputGroup.Text>
                    </InputGroup.Append>
                </InputGroup> 
            </Col>
        </Row>
        <Row>
            <Col lg={{span: 2, offset: 5}}>
                <Form.Group>
                    <Form.Control placeholder="密碼"></Form.Control>
                </Form.Group>
            </Col>
        </Row>
        <Row>
            <Col lg={{span: 2, offset: 5}} className="loginBtn">
                <Button variant="primary" type="submit">登入</Button>
            </Col>
        </Row>
        
        
        
    </Form>
    </Col>
    </Row>;

}

export default Login;
